Feline::

She breathed a visable sigh of releif. "Yes, I'm Feline."then the 
words hit her," Back to the Allience? Oh no, I can't go back. Not 
like this. Oh no," she looked paniced. "They can't see me like this.  
I'll be turned to scrap. Anybot that is deamed worthless is scrapped. 
I can't go back. Please, you said you were maximals once, don't you 
feel any compasion?Any sympathy? Please, don't send me back. Oh 
please," she pleaded with them in a desperate attempt to get them not 
to take her back to the base.  If only they would drop her off at a 
maximal base, she'd find her way from there.
"Oh, please, I beg you, don't send me back. Please." she said, tears 
of fright running down her chrome face plates.
